rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0001
rows.name: Ahh! Fresh air!

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0002
rows.name:
What's the matter?
You look like you were
suffocating in there.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0003
rows.name:
Laura-sama is always like this
when she's in a formal place.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0004
rows.name: Please don't mind her.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0005
rows.name: Hmm. What a pain.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0006
rows.name:
Hey! You're the one who
waited outside! That's not fair!

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0007
rows.name: Please don't say that.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0008
rows.name:
Because the person Minochi wanted
to see the least was in there.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0009
rows.name: The person he least wanted to see...?

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0010
rows.name: You don't mean... his Driver?!

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0012
rows.name: I-I'm sorry...

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0013
rows.name: It's fine. It's my own cowardice.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0014
rows.name:
From now on, we should also try
to make sure he and the
Deacon don't cross paths.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0015
rows.name: So what's the plan, Adel?

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0016
rows.name:
We came here to get ready
for Metsu's attack, but we have no idea
when he'll show up.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0017
rows.name:
Good point. First, let's take a walk
around the capital
and mingle with the locals.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0018
rows.name: Hey! Do we really have time for that?

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0019
rows.name:
It might not be pointless. If we get
a feel for the city's atmosphere,
we can sense when things change.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0020
rows.name: Shin is right.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0021
rows.name:
Plus, if we blend in with the people,
it'll probably be easier to get
their help when we need it.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0022
rows.name:
Though, maybe the great
Heaven's Holy Grail doesn't need
help from mere mortals.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0023
rows.name:
O-okay, I get it!
I was being thoughtless!

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0024
rows.name: Ganging up on me like this...

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0025
rows.name: No whining.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0026
rows.name:
I'm happy. Since we got more companions,
I've been able to see
all these different sides of you.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0027
rows.name: Well, I'm not happy about being seen.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0028
rows.name:
What's the big deal?
It just shows how much your
Driver cares about you.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0029
rows.name: I think so, too.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0030
rows.name:
Come on, since we're here,
let's all enjoy the atmosphere
of the capital.
